Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:06.89,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}なぜ 忘れたいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:12.87,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ねえ 思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:24.54,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あたたかい頬に降る 涙の願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:31.14,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}なぜ ふるえながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.70,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}今 求めあうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:43.33,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}君だけを何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:49.02,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}抱きしめたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:55.40,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蒼い星の海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:24:01.28,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波間に漂う羽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:07.34,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}消えてゆく哀しみは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.41,0:24:12.92,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}明日への祈りなの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:17.77,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Blueflow
Comment: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================↓ED(中)↓=================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:06.89,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为何想要忘却？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:12.87,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}请回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:24.54,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那温暖的脸颊上滑落而下的泪之请愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:31.14,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为何你在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.70,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}现在寻求着何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:43.33,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}只有你无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:49.02,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}都想与你相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:55.40,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蔚蓝的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:24:01.28,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波浪间漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:07.34,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}渐渐逝去的悲痛是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.41,0:24:12.92,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向着明日的祈祷


